query:
(select
                id,
                timestamp,
                serial_number,
                service,
                data
            from telemetry
            where
                service = 'plex'
                and serial_number = (select serial_number from device where id = $1)
            order by timestamp desc
            limit 1
            )
            UNION ALL
            (
            select
                id,
                timestamp,
                serial_number,
                service,
                data
            from telemetry
            where
                service = 'systemd1'
                and serial_number = (select serial_number from device where id = $1)
                and data->>'result' != 'done'
                and id < $2
            order by timestamp desc
            limit $3::int);
